"40:80:8" : {s: 40, a: 80, w: 8, r: "صدر", t: "صُدُورِكُمْ", l: "صَدْر", lc: 44, tl: "ṣudūrikum", lb: "বক্ষ, সিনা, অন্তর",e: "your breasts", b: "(যা) তোমাদের অন্তরে (আছে)", i: "dada kamu", f: 4, rm: "To return from, come back, proceed, issue or emanate from, go forward, advance or promote, come to pass, happen, emanate from, strike on the chest/breast, commence. Anything that fronts, or faces one; hence breast, chest or bosom [often meaning his mind]. The fore part of anything. Going, or turning back and away.", ag: "أسم مجرور وضمير متصل ", eg: "Noun Genitive case and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "GEN", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "يَصْدُرُ"},
